Detailed Description

Parameters:
LeftColumn Value that designates the text column at which the browser window will begin (left-most column).
RightColumn Value that designates the text column at which the browser window will end (right-most column).
TopRow Value that designates the text row from the top of the screen where the browser window will start.
BottomRow Value that designates the text row from the bottom of the screen where the browser window will end.
